### ============================================
### ADMIN AUTH
### ============================================

### Login Admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "{{email}}",
    "password": "{{password}}"
}

### Verificar Token
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### CATEGORIES
### ============================================

### Listar todas as categorias (público)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories

### Buscar categoria por ID (público)
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{categoryId}}

### Criar categoria (admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Cremes",
    "description": "Cremes faciais e corporais"
}

### Atualizar categoria (admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{categoryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Cremes Hidratantes",
    "description": "Cremes hidratantes para todos os tipos de pele"
}

### Deletar categoria (admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/categories/{{categoryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### PRODUCTS
### ============================================

### Listar todos os produtos (público)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products

### Buscar produto por ID (público)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productId}}

### Listar produtos deletados (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/deleted
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Criar produto (admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

Creme Hidratante Facial
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Creme hidratante para pele seca e sensível
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="price"

49.90
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="stock"

10
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category_id"

{{categoryId}}
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="active"

true
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="produto.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./assets/produto.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Atualizar produto (admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

Creme Hidratante Facial Premium
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

Creme hidratante premium para todos os tipos de pele
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="price"

59.90
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="stock"

15
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="category_id"

{{categoryId}}
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="active"

true
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="produto-novo.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./assets/produto-novo.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Deletar produto (soft delete - admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Restaurar produto (admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/products/{{productId}}/restore
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### REQUESTS (Solicitações)
### ============================================

### Criar solicitação (público)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/requests
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "customer_name": "Maria Silva",
    "customer_phone": "(11) 99999-9999",
    "products": [
        {
            "product_id": "{{productId}}",
            "name": "Creme Hidratante",
            "quantity": 2,
            "price": 49.90
        }
    ],
    "total": 99.80
}

### Listar todas as solicitações (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/requests
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Buscar solicitação por ID (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/requests/{{requestId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Listar solicitações deletadas (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/requests/deleted
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Atualizar status da solicitação (admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/requests/{{requestId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "completed"
}

### Deletar solicitação (soft delete - admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/requests/{{requestId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Restaurar solicitação (admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/requests/{{requestId}}/restore
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### HEALTH CHECK
### ============================================

### Verificar status da API
GET {{baseUrl}}/health